<subSubSection id="C34F64FB5578FF94528DBACDFB32FDE8" pageId="18" pageNumber="19" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BEA37705578FF94528DBACDFEBEFE65" blockId="18.[189,260,468,494]" box="[189,260,468,494]" pageId="18" pageNumber="19">
<heading id="D0A2801C5578FF94528DBACDFEBEFE65" bold="true" box="[189,260,468,494]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="18" pageNumber="19" reason="3">
<emphasis id="B921EB625578FF94528DBACDFEBEFE65" bold="true" box="[189,260,468,494]" pageId="18" pageNumber="19">Notes</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BEA37705578FF94528DB91AFB32FDE8" blockId="18.[189,1399,515,612]" pageId="18" pageNumber="19">
This species was originally described from a single specimen. The name ‘ 
<taxonomicName id="4C554CF35578FF94560BB91DFB73FD96" authorityName="Semenov Tjan-Shansky" authorityYear="1907" box="[1083,1225,516,541]" class="Insecta" family="Tenebrionidae" genus="Habrochiton" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="19" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="primaeveris">
<emphasis id="B921EB625578FF94560BB91DFB73FD96" box="[1083,1225,516,541]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="19">primaeveris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
’ is incorrectly written as “ 
<emphasis id="B921EB625578FF945375B93EFE64FDCB" box="[325,478,551,576]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="19">primaeverris</emphasis>
” in both editions of the catalogue of Palaearctic 
<taxonomicName id="4C554CF35578FF94562FB93FFB1AFDCB" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1758" box="[1055,1184,550,576]" class="Insecta" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="19" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="order">Coleoptera</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFC44A815578FF94569FB93FFAC8FDCB" author="Lobl I. &amp; Merkl O. &amp; Ando K. &amp; Bouchard P. &amp; Lillig M. &amp; Masumoto K. &amp; Schawaller W." box="[1199,1394,550,576]" pageId="18" pageNumber="19" pagination="105 - 352" refId="ref31535" refString="Lobl I., Merkl O., Ando K., Bouchard P., Lillig M., Masumoto K. &amp; Schawaller W. 2008. Family Tenebrionidae Latreille, 1802. In: Lobl I. &amp; Smetana A. (eds) Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera. Vol. 5: Tenebrionoidea: 105 - 352. Apollo books, Stenstrup." type="book chapter" year="2008">
Löbl 
<emphasis id="B921EB625578FF9456C0B93EFA96FDCB" box="[1264,1324,550,576]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="19">et al.</emphasis>
2008
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFC44A815578FF94528DB953FE38FDE8" author="Iwan D. &amp; Lobl I. &amp; Bouchard P. &amp; Bousquet Y. &amp; Kaminski M. J. &amp; Merkl O. &amp; Ando K. &amp; Schawaller W." box="[189,386,585,612]" pageId="18" pageNumber="19" pagination="104 - 476" refId="ref30795" refString="Iwan D., Lobl I., Bouchard P., Bousquet Y., Kaminski M. J., Merkl O., Ando K. &amp; Schawaller W. 2020. Family Tenebrionidae Latreille, 1802. In: Iwan D. &amp; Lobl I. (eds) Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera. Vol. 5: Tenebrionoidea: 104 - 476. Brill, Leiden. https: // doi. org / 10.1163 / 9789004434998" type="book chapter" year="2020">
Iwan 
<emphasis id="B921EB625578FF9452CFB953FE80FDE8" box="[255,314,585,611]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="19">et al.</emphasis>
2020
</bibRefCitation>
). Semenov Tjan-Shansky used the original epithet ‘ 
<emphasis id="B921EB625578FF9451EFB953FBCDFDE8" box="[991,1143,586,612]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="19">primae -veris</emphasis>
’.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
